{{Quote|Those streaks of light are ''cosmic rays&hellip;'' flashing across the universe&hellip; responding only to ''luck''!|Luke Skywalker|<ref name="Gambler's World">"[[Gambler's World]]"</ref>}}
'''Cosmic Chance''' was a game of chance. Players would use their "luck" to influence [[Cosmic ray/Legends|cosmic rays]] that flashed across [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]], in hopes of hitting targets. Other gamblers would bet on whether they would score or not. Scoring was very rare, and nobody had ever scored more than twice. [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] was very good at Cosmic Chance.

